    <p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/learning-training"  data-drop-content="drop-nav-2" class="medium expand button">Learning and training</a>
      <span class="arrow"></span>    </p>
        <ul class="small-block-grid-3 drop-content" id="drop-nav-2">
