<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    <div class="full-title with-title-branding">
      <div class="title-branding"><a href="/taxonomy/term/868"><img src="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/styles/16x9_small/public/sight-and-sound-logo-280x69.png?itok=AEegRSbk" alt="" /></a></div>
  
  <h1>
          Divining the real: the leaps of faith in André Bazin’s film criticism    
    
      </h1>

  
  
        <div class="copy">
              <div class="intro"><p>André Bazin, the high priest of realism, practically invented film studies. It&#8217;s time he was rehabilitated from postmodern sneers, argues Peter Matthews.</p>
<p>This piece from our <a href="http://old.bfi.org.uk/sightandsound/issue/199908">August 1999 issue</a> is republished in honour of Bazin&#8217;s centenary.</p>
</div>
            
      
              <p class="author-data">
          <span class="author"> Peter  Matthews  </span><br /><span class="date"><time datetime="2018-04-18">18 April 2018</time></span>        </p>
      
      
          </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    
  <ul class="share">
          <li class="facebook_share"><div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/features/andre-bazin-divining-real-film-criticism-overview" data-layout="button_count"></div>
</li>
          <li class="field_tweetbutton"><div class="tweetbutton-tweet tweetbutton"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" data-size="medium" data-count="horizontal" data-via="SightSoundmag" data-related=":" data-text="Divining the real: the leaps of faith in #AndréBazin’s film criticism" data-counturl="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/features/andre-bazin-divining-real-film-criticism-overview" data-url="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/features/andre-bazin-divining-real-film-criticism-overview" data-lang="" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a></div></li>
          <li class="pinterest"><a href="//pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/features/andre-bazin-divining-real-film-criticism-overview&description=Divining the real: the leaps of faith in André Bazin’s film criticism&media=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/news/andre-bazin-001-camera-portrait-CROP.jpg" data-pin-do="buttonPin" data-pin-config="beside" data-pin-zero="true"><img src="//assets.pinterest.com/images/pidgets/pin_it_button.png" /></a></li>
