                      <p class="authors"> Miriam  Bale  ,  Jemma  Desai  ,  Violet  Lucca  ,  Jonathan  Rosenbaum  ,  Francine  Stock  ,  Matthew  Sweet  ,  Ben  Walters  ,  Rob  Winter  </p>
                  </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </li>
      </ul>

  
</div>
